  "type": "spr",
  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The graph of <math alttext=\"9 x minus 10 y equals 19\"><mrow><mn>9</mn></mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mrow><mn>10</mn></mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mn>19</mn></mrow></math> is translated down <math alttext=\"4\"><mn>4</mn>\n</math> units in the <em>xy</em>-plane. What is the <em>x</em>-coordinate of the <em>x</em>-intercept of the resulting graph?</p>",
